think, be here, as well.

00:09:06.850 --> 00:09:08.410
But after we wrote
"Half the Sky,"

00:09:08.410 --> 00:09:10.290
and after the "Half
the Sky" documentary

00:09:10.290 --> 00:09:13.524
that Mira had also
worked on, then that

00:09:13.524 --> 00:09:15.440
had really focused on
empowering women abroad.

00:09:15.440 --> 00:09:17.689
And after that, we got a
couple of kinds of questions.

00:09:17.689 --> 00:09:20.710
One, what about the situation
right here in the US?

00:09:20.710 --> 00:09:23.200
And secondly, so what can I do?

00:09:23.200 --> 00:09:24.460
What are the solutions?

00:09:24.460 --> 00:09:28.260
And we wanted to
come back and look

00:09:28.260 --> 00:09:31.410
at ways one can
make a difference.

00:09:31.410 --> 00:09:35.900
It does seem to us that,
by and large, people

00:09:35.900 --> 00:09:40.480
do want to find a little
more purpose in life,

00:09:40.480 --> 00:09:43.540
make a difference-- especially
millennials, for that matter.

00:09:43.540 --> 00:09:46.160
And that there really is
evidence now about what works,

00:09:46.160 --> 00:09:48.040
what doesn't work.

00:09:48.040 --> 00:09:50.920
And that there
are-- sometimes it

00:09:50.920 --> 00:09:55.280
becomes a little bit too easy
to point to problems abroad,

00:09:55.280 --> 00:09:59.000
