them against each other

00:10:01.290 --> 00:10:05.390
and say, either we should
solve our own problems first,

00:10:05.390 --> 00:10:11.820
before worrying about Tanzania,
or to say the opposite--

00:10:11.820 --> 00:10:13.900
that we should just
focus on problems abroad.

00:10:13.900 --> 00:10:16.070
There are huge problems
both here and abroad,

00:10:16.070 --> 00:10:18.560
and we wanted to
offer some windows

00:10:18.560 --> 00:10:22.330
into how to address them.

