00:24:50.520 --> 00:24:53.130
probably from untreated
ear infections.

00:24:53.130 --> 00:24:56.270
And so they weren't caught.

00:24:56.270 --> 00:24:59.150
He wouldn't get a
hearing screening.

00:24:59.150 --> 00:25:02.150
And so as his brain
is developing,

00:25:02.150 --> 00:25:05.310
he's not getting
any auditory input,

00:25:05.310 --> 00:25:07.660
so that he doesn't
develop speech.

00:25:07.660 --> 00:25:11.550
And finally, it's caught
later on by Save the Children.

00:25:11.550 --> 00:25:13.800
Thank God they were
there to do it.

00:25:13.800 --> 00:25:16.200
And we still don't know
whether he will ever fully

00:25:16.200 --> 00:25:17.640
be able to recover.

00:25:17.640 --> 00:25:21.610
An idea that this happens,
that a kid like Johnny

00:25:21.610 --> 00:25:23.860
can fall through the
cracks in this country,

00:25:23.860 --> 00:25:29.370
through something as simple as
missing a hearing screening,

00:25:29.370 --> 00:25:32.970
is just shattering when you
see a little kid like that.

00:25:32.970 --> 00:25:37.136
And I hope that one thing that
viewers will get from "A Path

00:25:37.136 --> 00:25:38.510
Appears" when they
see them is we

00:25:38.510 --> 00:25:40.922
have this narrative in this
country about how poverty

00:25:40.922 --> 00:25:42.380
is about personal
irresponsibility.

00:25:45.330 --> 00:25:48.046
There's no doubt that
that is sometimes true,

00:25:48.046 --> 00:25:49.920
that there are certainly
some poor people who

00:25:49.920 --> 00:25:53.140
are irresponsible, and there
is self-destructive behavior

00:25:53.140 --> 00:25:55.320
that sometimes
goes with poverty.

00:25:55.320 --> 00:25:57.310
But not always.

00:25:57.310 --> 00:26:01.520
And you get a four-year-old
kid who has done nothing wrong.

00:26:01.520 --> 00:26:05.110
And yet he is going to
be disadvantaged, perhaps

00:26:05.110 --> 00:26:08.360
for the rest of his life,
because we dropped the ball.

00:26:08.360 --> 00:26:10.439
We as a society dropped
the ball in providing

00:26:10.439 --> 00:26:11.230
hearing screenings.

00:26:11.230 --> 00:26:14.780
And that's an irresponsibility
that is not Johnny's.

00:26:14.780 --> 00:26:16.970
It's ours.

00:26:16.970 --> 00:26:18.780
CHERIE HANNOUCHE:
I think that story

00:26:18.780 --> 00:26:22.970
and obviously, Savannah's story,
as well, are so shattering.

00:26:22.970 --> 00:26:27.610
