there are so many similarities.

00:30:34.020 --> 00:30:38.130
And a lot of them
have to do with what

00:30:38.130 --> 00:30:40.620
if you could intervene
a little earlier?

00:30:40.620 --> 00:30:43.220
What if you can remove
some of the vulnerability

00:30:43.220 --> 00:30:45.170
that they're facing
as a young child?

00:30:45.170 --> 00:30:48.380
What if the moms, when
they're having the babies,

00:30:48.380 --> 00:30:50.515
know how to raise their
babies, or give them

00:30:50.515 --> 00:30:53.460
a better shot at both
medical care or education?

00:30:53.460 --> 00:30:56.430
I think it has an impact on
all of these different things

00:30:56.430 --> 00:31:00.060
that we are talking about
and are worried about.

00:31:00.060 --> 00:31:03.650
So we should invest earlier.

00:31:03.650 --> 00:31:04.650
CHERIE HANNOUCHE: Great.

00:31:04.650 --> 00:31:07.191
Well, before-- I want to make
