00:34:46.270 --> 00:34:47.960
by focusing on the demand side?

00:34:47.960 --> 00:34:51.860
And are you hopeful that
that's an innovation that

00:34:51.860 --> 00:34:54.960
may be helpful in stemming
the tide of the trafficking

00:34:54.960 --> 00:34:56.594
trend in the US and abroad?

00:34:56.594 --> 00:34:58.260
NICHOLAS KRISTOF:
It's a great question.

00:34:58.260 --> 00:35:01.390
And indeed, I think that
focusing on the demand side

00:35:01.390 --> 00:35:03.860
is-- there's no
silver bullet here.

00:35:03.860 --> 00:35:05.300
But there's silver buckshot.

00:35:05.300 --> 00:35:07.471
And that's one of the
elements of silver buckshot

00:35:07.471 --> 00:35:09.220
that can make a
difference on trafficking.

00:35:09.220 --> 00:35:13.660
I'm generally a believer that
ending impunity for problems

00:35:13.660 --> 00:35:17.300
is hugely important.

00:35:17.300 --> 00:35:19.844
One of the things that
isn't much realized

00:35:19.844 --> 00:35:22.260
is that there has actually
been, over the last generation,

00:35:22.260 --> 00:35:27.010
huge progress in the US on both
domestic violence and rape,

00:35:27.010 --> 00:35:28.330
as best we can measure them.

00:35:28.330 --> 00:35:30.280
And the numbers are problematic.

00:35:30.280 --> 00:35:34.130
But using victimization surveys
it looks as if both of them

00:35:34.130 --> 00:35:37.250
have fallen by more than 50%
over the last generation.

00:35:37.250 --> 00:35:38.260
And why is that?

00:35:38.260 --> 00:35:41.050
A generation ago, there
was 100% impunity.

00:35:41.050 --> 00:35:42.920
A husband could completely
beat up his wife,

00:35:42.920 --> 00:35:44.510
a boyfriend completely
beat up his girlfriend.

00:35:44.510 --> 00:35:46.260
The police just
would not intervene.

00:35:46.260 --> 00:35:49.750
And most rapes are people
who know each other.

00:35:49.750 --> 00:35:53.069
It's a boyfriend/girlfriend
situation, or former boyfriend,

00:35:53.069 --> 00:35:53.860
whatever it may be.

00:35:53.860 --> 00:35:55.400
And again, there,
in that situation

00:35:55.400 --> 00:35:57.200
was almost complete impunity.

00:35:57.200 --> 00:35:59.610
Now we know that
there is still a lot

00:35:59.610 --> 00:36:01.800
of impunity in that situation.

00:36:01.800 --> 00:36:08.180
But now there are enough guys
who, even though they've drunk

00:36:08.180 --> 00:36:14.750
too much, they-- when this
girl says, no, stop here,

00:36:14.750 --> 00:36:16.530
something still goes
on in their brain.

00:36:16.530 --> 00:36:18.240
And they think there
might be a risk.

00:36:18.240 --> 00:36:22.240
And that's why those
victimization rates

00:36:22.240 --> 00:36:23.360
have gone down.

00:36:23.360 --> 00:36:26.780
In the case of
trafficking, again, we

00:36:26.780 --> 00:36:27.780
don't have good numbers.

00:36:27.780 --> 00:36:30.930
But a rough estimate
is about 300,000 men

00:36:30.930 --> 00:36:33.600
will buy sex today
somewhere in the US.

00:36:33.600 --> 00:36:36.970
Virtually none of
them will be arrested.

00:36:36.970 --> 00:36:39.000
You're more likely to
be hit by lightning

00:36:39.000 --> 00:36:41.350
than you are to be
arrested while buying sex.

00:36:41.350 --> 00:36:44.560
So there is essentially
no risk to you.

00:36:44.560 --> 00:36:47.970
A lot of those men
have a lot to lose

00:36:47.970 --> 00:36:52.210
if they were arrested
for buying sex.

00:36:52.210 --> 00:36:54.060
They have reputations.

00:36:54.060 --> 00:36:55.600
It would be a very bad thing.

00:36:55.600 --> 00:36:59.290
If there were just a 1% or 2%
risk that they might actually

00:36:59.290 --> 00:37:01.840
be arrested, I think
they wouldn't buy sex.

00:37:01.840 --> 00:37:04.560
And I think you
would, in that case,

00:37:04.560 --> 00:37:08.110
see a significant
drop in demand.

00:37:08.110 --> 00:37:12.580
And in that case, there would
be fewer women trafficked.

00:37:12.580 --> 00:37:16.390
And going after johns
is actually pretty easy.

00:37:16.390 --> 00:37:19.050
We have a segment in the
doc where we, essentially--

00:37:19.050 --> 00:37:21.700
the police department
posts an ad on Backpage

00:37:21.700 --> 00:37:24.420
and books a hotel room.

00:37:24.420 --> 00:37:27.630
